ui (2.14) stable;

  * Add ui:updateRate property.
  * Add idle interface so native UIs and foreign toolkits can drive their event
    loops.

 -- David Robillard <d@drobilla.net>  Mon, 18 Mar 2013 00:00:00 +0000

